OL,3,C'Serious security breach' after break-
OL,4,Cin at hospital's mortuary
OL,6,FSecurity has been increased at a
OL,7,Fhospital's mortuary after a patient
OL,8,Fbroke in through a locked door.
OL,10,FNorth Bristol NHS Trust (NBT) said no
OL,11,Fcold storage units or human remains
OL,12,Fwere accessed in what has been classed
OL,13,Fas a "serious security breach" at
OL,14,FSouthmead Hospital in Bristol.
OL,16,FThe incident, which happened in
OL,17,FFebruary, was discussed at an NBT
OL,18,Fboard meeting on Thursday 30 May,
OL,19,Fduring which it was confirmed the
OL,20,Finvestigation into the break-in has
OL,21,Fnow closed.
