OL,3,C'Serious security breach' after break-
OL,4,Cin at hospital's mortuary
OL,6,F"An incident occurred when an NHS
OL,7,Fpatient with complex care needs was
OL,8,Fable to temporarily gain entry to
OL,9,Fareas within the mortuary facility
OL,10,Fafter forcing doors that were locked,"
OL,11,Fa spokesperson for the trust said.
OL,13,F"Through detailed CCTV monitoring we
OL,14,Fcan confirm that at no point were any
OL,15,Frefrigerated or frozen storage units
OL,16,Fholding human tissue breached and, as
OL,17,Fsuch, we can give an absolute
OL,18,Fassurance that no remains were
OL,19,Faccessed at any time."
