OL,7,Fshortly after breaking into the
OL,8,Fhospital's mortuary.
OL,10,FThe trust which runs the hospital
OL,11,Fadded it has improved security
OL,12,Fmeasures at Southmead Hospital to
OL,13,Fprevent a repeat incident.
