OL,3,C'Serious security breach' after break-
OL,4,Cin at hospital's mortuary
OL,6,F"We have significantly increased both
OL,7,Fthe strength and number of locked
OL,8,Fdoors that protect the mortuary and
OL,9,Fhave put in place additional measures
OL,10,Fto ensure each area of the mortuary
OL,11,Fcan be secured independently of any
OL,12,Fother ` so a breach in one will not
OL,13,Faffect another," an NBT spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"We have introduced enhanced measures
OL,17,Fto increase the speed at which our on-
OL,18,Fsite security teams are able to
OL,19,Frespond to alerts in or near the
OL,20,Fmortuary," they added.
