OL,3,C'Serious security breach' after break-
OL,4,Cin at hospital's mortuary
OL,6,FAn investigation into the incident was
OL,7,Flaunched by the Human Tissue Authority
OL,8,F(HTA), a Department of Health and
OL,9,FSocial Care quango, and has now closed.
OL,11,FChief executive Maria Kane's report to
OL,12,Fthe NBT board meeting confirmed the
OL,13,Fincident was "classified as a HTA
OL,14,FReportable Incident and categorised as
OL,15,Fa serious security breach."
OL,17,FThe report added: "The HTA has
OL,18,Facknowledged the evidence submitted
OL,19,Fand all of the corrective actions and
OL,20,Fmitigations that have taken place and
OL,21,Fhas now closed the incident."
