OL,6,FGiving a verbal update to the board,
OL,7,FMs Kane said: "We are noting this
OL,8,Fpublicly that the Human Tissue
OL,9,FAuthority (has carried out a) review
OL,10,Fof a mortuary incident, they have
OL,11,Facknowledged our evidence and
OL,12,Fmitigating actions and have now
OL,13,Fdecided that they are now happy to
OL,14,Fclose the incident.
OL,16,F"But there has been learning from
OL,17,Fthat, clearly, and we will continue to
OL,18,Fmonitor that and have put in place
OL,19,Fadditional contract expectations from
OL,20,Four providers."
